{"data":[{"name":"102:1","price":"Bermegah-megahan telah melalaikan kamu1599,","arabic":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6169,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1599.  Maksudnya bermegah-megahan dalam soal banyak anak, harta, pengikut, kemuliaan, dan seumpamanya telah melalaikan kamu dari ketaatan. ","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:2","price":"sampai kamu masuk ke dalam kubur.","arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6170,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:3","price":"Janganlah begitu, kelak kamu akan mengetahui (akibat perbuatanmu itu),","arabic":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6171,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:4","price":"dan janganlah begitu, kelak kamu akan mengetahui.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6172,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:5","price":"Janganlah begitu, jika kamu mengetahui dengan pengetahuan yang yakin,","arabic":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6173,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:6","price":"niscaya kamu benar-benar akan melihat neraka Jaḥīm,","arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6174,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:7","price":"dan sesungguhnya kamu benar-benar akan melihatnya dengan ainul yakin1600.","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6175,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1600.  Ainul yakin artinya melihat dengan mata kepala sendiri sehingga menimbulkan keyakinan yang kuat. ","lang":"id"},{"name":"102:8","price":"kemudian kamu pasti akan ditanyai pada hari itu tentang kenikmatan (yang kamu megah-megahkan di dunia itu).","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6176,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"id"}],"chapter":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur","Chapter At-Takathur","Takathur","Surah Takathur","Chapter Takathur","At Takathur","Surah At Takathur","Chapter At Takathur","Surah 102","Chapter 102","The Rivalry","التكاثر"]}